Class DMTLParser

java.lang.Object
  metaface.interaction.DMTLParser
public class DMTLParser
extends Object

DMTLParser takes DMTL documents and transforms them into an internal storage format (KnowledgeBase). This format is then used by the InteractionManager. DMTL is defined by the following DMTL structure:

See the DMTL DTD or and example file .
